{"tid":1550073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"口號與精神意義問題","createTime":"2019-09-07T14:15:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:48.000Z","uid":225887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ed4f6cec93c3cfe95008cb3758001402d0b13bef","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"經過左咁多場被打壓 死黑警愈黎愈癲既獸化<br />\n口號既作用本來係戰場上可以話係一個必須品<br />\n因為佢起既作用極大心理振奮既作用<br />\n亦當然對對方造成心理壓力<br />\n<br />\n鑑於現時既口號既作用已經偏麻目 或<br />\n做唔到振奮效果 可以稍為建議除左骨幹口號<br />\nE.g 五大訴求 缺一不可 and 光復香港 時代革命 外<br />\n其他都要考慮改進<br />\n<br />\n例如 係和理非可以嗌香港人加油<br />\n但你無理由同警察對峙都叫香港人加油<br />\n應該叫 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 反抗</span><br />\n<br />\n又例如 面對黑警叫佢地黑社會都已經影響唔到佢地<br />\n或者呢句野本身攻擊力太低<br />\n我地應該叫 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警 強姦犯 殺人犯 死淫蟲</span><br />\n或者直接關心佢地老婆現況等<br />\n<br />\n我知一時三刻改唔易 大家覺得點"},{"pid":"611a17ba61bc345e9ec7875c41021ec0f6c92937","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:15:45.000Z","msg":"自推十野"},{"pid":"2b22910f17ab265aebd593aa3bcbbfee0964f8a7","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:15:59.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗1"},{"pid":"0eea8afa761a079ea37ca80387ad8cb6f794e898","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:16:09.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗2"},{"pid":"19ef6f2341411b06eca43f3641e0c260e5f4073f","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:16:19.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗3"},{"pid":"e8acfaac26e36b9f9da2e79006131cde09c8e234","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:16:30.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗4"},{"pid":"2a0685134f08bcac1bccf50ecaf1ac12cc60907c","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:16:44.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗5"},{"pid":"a9d1c2f8303d3ae3581048d4091ce73bb677b143","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:00.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗6"},{"pid":"c472a7ae64c385a03614cb58b882f3ec29626a1a","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:15.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗7"},{"pid":"c4a822b29f635d16002d211133e6ffef7c5b4ab2","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗8"},{"pid":"a503238560fb97aa893b94349ab42e147e819f2f","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:35.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗9"},{"pid":"f742fbe4181ebd197dd24daa35e7a59d5e3a16c8","tid":1550073,"uid":157857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1de367369cdd2eb8af0ef84ff16a0b0ae42bf4ea","tid":1550073,"uid":225887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T14:17:48.000Z","msg":"香港人反抗10"}]}